org.apache.james.imap.message.request

Class AbstractMailboxSelectionRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.james.imap.message.request.AbstractImapRequest
      • org.apache.james.imap.message.request.AbstractMailboxSelectionRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ImapMessage, ImapRequest
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExamineRequest, SelectRequest

    public abstract class AbstractMailboxSelectionRequest
extends AbstractImapRequest
    ImapRequest which selects a Mailbox. This supports also the CONDSTORE and the QRESYNC extension
